title: [Maelstrom Bay, Cemetery]
description: The center of the cemetery is marked by a statue of robed woman on a pedestal surrounded by dirt ruts that circle her once, then split away to the east.  Clusters of lilies grow around the base of the pedestal and fill the area with a sweet, rich aroma.  Headstones of varying sizes and makes populate the grass expanse up to the edge of the bluff to the north, some nearly invisible behind tall grasses and weeds.
paths: Obvious paths: east, south, west, northwest
